        <description>&lt;img src="https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/1740150398299.jpeg" alt="Featured image of post 使用虚拟机创建软（旁）路由实现魔法上网" /&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;准备工作&#34;&gt;准备工作
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;需要有一个能够24小时开机的主机，比如在Nas或者Server上创建。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;创建虚拟机&#34;&gt;创建虚拟机
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;以我使用的群晖举例，首先在虚拟机的映像中选择硬盘映像，其他虚拟机大部分同理。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-13-29.png&#34;
	width=&#34;885&#34;
	height=&#34;520&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-13-29_hu_6de6d3bba868773a.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-13-29_hu_db5df436faffa0e2.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;170&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;408px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;导入一个软路由的镜像，这里以openwrt高大全版本举例。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-14-08.png&#34;
	width=&#34;690&#34;
	height=&#34;493&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-14-08_hu_73670da7f316f9ef.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-14-08_hu_a37c3bd70a7354d6.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;139&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;335px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;再回到虚拟机界面选择导入。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-16-22.png&#34;
	width=&#34;710&#34;
	height=&#34;521&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-16-22_hu_82fff47edbcecddc.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-16-22_hu_78c8d52c92e4cb20.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;136&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;327px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;从硬盘映像导入。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-27.png&#34;
	width=&#34;697&#34;
	height=&#34;532&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-27_hu_69c007b7b188dac7.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-27_hu_6724ae511895ee46.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;131&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;314px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;规格默认即可。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-42.png&#34;
	width=&#34;698&#34;
	height=&#34;539&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-42_hu_a1dac99d988d9788.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-42_hu_2b82863adb9a2231.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;129&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;310px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在存储空间里选择刚刚导入的硬盘镜像。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-55.png&#34;
	width=&#34;704&#34;
	height=&#34;526&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-55_hu_654f38073ee35911.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-19-55_hu_c91f793600d54d74.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;321px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在网卡界面选择e1000（兼容性更好些）。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-29-19.png&#34;
	width=&#34;700&#34;
	height=&#34;535&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-29-19_hu_92ce63adc0df6949.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-29-19_hu_c98a3b21e60755ff.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;130&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;314px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;其余设置默认即可，&lt;strong&gt;自动启动&lt;/strong&gt;按需选择即可。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后勾选创建完后打开虚拟机&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-21-29.png&#34;
	width=&#34;689&#34;
	height=&#34;526&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-21-29_hu_7b0deaeb287bd444.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-21-29_hu_ec60be64c7cc24dd.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;130&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;314px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后回到虚拟机界面点击&lt;strong&gt;连接&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;配置软路由&#34;&gt;配置软路由
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;命令行配置&#34;&gt;命令行配置
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;来到以下界面后，按任意键位（只要不是系统键位都行）。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-26-54.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2445&#34;
	height=&#34;1358&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-26-54_hu_9b199dacb9b4fcde.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-26-54_hu_174ea0cb0420fc8b.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;180&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;432px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;进入到以下界面&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-34-33.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2445&#34;
	height=&#34;1358&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-34-33_hu_5a303a02eb857e6d.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-34-33_hu_4b38873f898756b8.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;180&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;432px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选择1，然后输入你的内网任意未被使用的IP地址，如果不确定，可以打开自己电脑的命令行窗口输入&lt;code&gt;ipconfig&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-40-33.png&#34;
	width=&#34;515&#34;
	height=&#34;73&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-40-33_hu_7511edee6a37f4a5.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-40-33_hu_1b6096472d364ca1.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;705&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1693px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;通常前三位就是局域网固定IP。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;输入完后回车，再输入4然后会确认是否需要重启，填入y重启。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;网页配置&#34;&gt;网页配置
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;在浏览器中输入刚才选择的IP地址，进入页面&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-48-23.png&#34;
	width=&#34;686&#34;
	height=&#34;597&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-48-23_hu_52d64f6045c9455d.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-48-23_hu_6deea8c9e098235b.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;114&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;275px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;默认无密码，进去后请先根据提示更改密码。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;更改密码后来到网络接口页面&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-51-41.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2434&#34;
	height=&#34;758&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-51-41_hu_22de2f6079c24cb0.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-51-41_hu_c0c6982f6fb1d523.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;321&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;770px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;填写网关以及关闭IPV6和DHCP&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-52-31.png&#34;
	width=&#34;852&#34;
	height=&#34;1091&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-52-31_hu_6d8d6ffc740d9d9f.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-52-31_hu_e5f33ef11fa2b95c.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;78&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;187px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-52-45.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2215&#34;
	height=&#34;201&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-52-45_hu_a259b5c621c34ecf.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-52-45_hu_7b82e866d52a2096.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;1101&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;2644px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-53-00.png&#34;
	width=&#34;858&#34;
	height=&#34;454&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-53-00_hu_ce14f5579daa2799.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-53-00_hu_b7864d9583506ba6.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;188&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;453px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后记得保存并应用接口配置就算完成了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;魔法配置&#34;&gt;魔法配置
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;能够使用的有很多种，以我常用的小猫咪举例。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;进入后可以先不下载内核。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;_2025-03-05_23-49-22.png&#34;  /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;先进行以下更改&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-50-24.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1933&#34;
	height=&#34;1080&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-50-24_hu_77d70adc1994e599.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-50-24_hu_8d7234d70af3d4d.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;178&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;429px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-51-04.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1559&#34;
	height=&#34;911&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-51-04_hu_fa3efedae62488cf.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-51-04_hu_2b31945481a65551.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;171&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;410px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;来到流量控制界面&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-54-18.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1463&#34;
	height=&#34;733&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-54-18_hu_20cb7a73e980c6ca.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-54-18_hu_54a18752f7d588d0.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;199&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;479px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;来到覆写设置界面，需要把开发者选项中27行这串代码注释去掉，随后把下方自定义上游DNS服务全部取消勾选。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-56-11.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2188&#34;
	height=&#34;1180&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-56-11_hu_119eacbf452748b3.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-56-11_hu_cc4fbdb625a98953.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;185&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;445px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;覆写设置的DNS设置&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-56-48.png&#34;
	width=&#34;897&#34;
	height=&#34;912&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-56-48_hu_9af3a6aa8214700.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-56-48_hu_a8891dec8681457b.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;98&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;236px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-58-57.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1013&#34;
	height=&#34;913&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-58-57_hu_54745e10ee0f3cd1.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-58-57_hu_394c96ea6e9a6c1d.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;110&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;266px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;配置文件设置&#34;&gt;配置文件设置
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;建议先用自带电脑把clash的配置拉取过来后新建一个&lt;code&gt;config.yaml&lt;/code&gt;文件，然后把配置信息填入进去保存后再上传（原因是因为软路由这里订阅拉取经常拉取不到，如果能够拉取可以直接填写订阅地址即可）&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_00-00-16.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1025&#34;
	height=&#34;747&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_00-00-16_hu_51b844dda8a67c10.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_00-00-16_hu_4ae99f96d1e54c00.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;137&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;329px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-59-38.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1753&#34;
	height=&#34;362&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-59-38_hu_dca79859d9d744a0.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-05_23-59-38_hu_32f156482a3c8d3f.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;484&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1162px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;更新内核&#34;&gt;更新内核
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;如果直接在界面下载无法更新内核，这时候需要用到ssh来进行上传文件&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;连接ssh，如果使用高大全版本则输入&lt;code&gt;9&lt;/code&gt;退出菜单,其他版本则忽略。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_00-21-31.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1022&#34;
	height=&#34;595&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_00-21-31_hu_19f1dc2e7966c168.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_00-21-31_hu_cbdb2c9d39418296.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;171&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;412px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;tun模式内核默认在&lt;code&gt;/etc/openclash/core/clash_tun&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;可以使用ftp工具将文件上传至这个目录，随后重新在插件见面启动即可。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;使用指南&#34;&gt;使用指南
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;在网络节目修改以下信息即可&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_01-06-18.png&#34;
	width=&#34;450&#34;
	height=&#34;502&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_01-06-18_hu_1fe086e4c2084ef6.png 480w, https://web.yuzia.fun/p/virtual-pc-deploy-router/_2025-03-06_01-06-18_hu_d1679ad89516b297.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;89&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;215px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;所有端同理，还有进阶玩法可以不用一个个修改，不过如果软路由损坏会导致家庭网络崩溃，无特殊需求可以不部署（后续也许会出一期qwq）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;疑难杂症&#34;&gt;疑难杂症
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;创建软路由的本体是否能够填写来进行魔法上网？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;答：虽然网络上有说不可以，但以我自己实测是可以使用的&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
